      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior upholstery has some visible wear and minor staining. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it lacks the smoothness of a newer model and may require routine maintenance soon. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its years of reliable service.",
