    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. The exterior is well-preserved, showing only minor signs of use such as small paint chips and light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car drives smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
